---
title: Orchestrator Guard Integration — Retry State Machine
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> InputCheck

    InputCheck: Input Guard Check
    note right of InputCheck
        POST /classify role input
        Timeout GUARD_TIMEOUT_S (10s)
    end note

    state input_result <<choice>>
    InputCheck --> input_result

    input_result --> BlockRequest: unsafe or unreachable
    input_result --> ProceedRAG: safe

    BlockRequest: Return Apology
    note right of BlockRequest
        APOLOGY_MESSAGE
        Skip entire RAG pipeline
        Guard unreachable = fail closed
    end note
    BlockRequest --> [*]

    ProceedRAG: Execute RAG Pipeline
    ProceedRAG --> OutputCheck: LLM answer generated

    OutputCheck: Output Guard Check (Attempt 1)
    note right of OutputCheck
        POST /classify role output
        prompt = original user query
    end note

    state output_result <<choice>>
    OutputCheck --> output_result

    output_result --> DeliverAnswer: safe
    output_result --> RetryWithFeedback: unsafe

    RetryWithFeedback: Retry LLM with Safety Feedback
    note right of RetryWithFeedback
        Append safety feedback to prompt
        Regenerate answer via LLM
    end note

    RetryWithFeedback --> OutputCheck2: new answer

    OutputCheck2: Output Guard Check (Attempt 2)

    state output_result2 <<choice>>
    OutputCheck2 --> output_result2

    output_result2 --> DeliverAnswer: safe
    output_result2 --> BlockResponse: still unsafe

    BlockResponse: Return Apology
    note right of BlockResponse
        Max 1 retry allowed
        Still unsafe after retry = apology
    end note
    BlockResponse --> [*]

    DeliverAnswer: Deliver Answer + Citations
    DeliverAnswer --> [*]
